Dear Students Greetings Hope you are all safe and doing well We are very happy to inform you that Center for Data Sciences and Applied Machine Learning CDSAML Department of Computer Science Engineering PES University is offering projects to 2nd and 4th semester students CSE only as a part of summer internship during June July 2021 In this regard Interested students are hereby informed to register by filling the google form Link for the same is provided below Kindly Read through Guidelines before filling the form Form Link httpsformsgleHZeazn8SuHkmDmj77 Guidelines Students having CGPA of 85 and above can only register Form a group Team of 3 members Min and Max team size is 3 Team members must be from the same campus Only 1 member from the team will register on behalf of the entire team done to avoid duplicate entries Students with their own laptop and good Internet facility only should register The Last date for registration is 2062021 wednesday 10 PM Note Number of teams selected will be based on the bandwidth of faculty members and the infrastructure availability Internship duration can be extended to accommodate the ESA Schedule For any queries you can mail to

Dear Jason Im writing to resign from my position as customer service representative effective August 14 2020 Ive recently decided to go back to school and my program starts in early September Im tendering my resignation now so that I can be as helpful as possible to you during the transition Ive truly enjoyed my time working with you and everyone else on our team at LMK Its rare to find a customer service role that offers as much opportunity to grow and learn as well as such a positive inspiring team of people to grow and learn with Im particularly grateful for your guidance while I was considering furthering my education Your support has meant so much to me Please let me know if theres anything I can do to help you find and train my replacement Thanks and best wishes Nicole Thomas signature hard copy letter Nicole Thomas
